{"tid":462904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"官問當時有沒有警員以警棍打人  朱：就我所見無，我睇唔哂成個現場","createTime":"2017-11-09T03:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T04:35:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"08cbfd5656f51a72f40d427d980913b43ccba39f","tid":462904,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171109/large/1510198424_0bd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F1510198424_0bd3.jpg&h=880b8907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【11:30】<br />\n朱經緯稱，約當晚10時半前，警方封路後部分人企圖衝出馬路，警員要「掹警棍才能恢復秩序」。裁判官錢禮要求朱澄清「掹」的意思是否有實際使用?朱表示有用於「check drills」去推走人群，也有警員以戒備姿態。錢官再重申問題，是問警棍與人群有沒有身體接觸，朱首先答「無」，後來改口說「有啲」，因為「check drills」也會有身體接觸。錢官直視朱經緯，說她的問題其實相當清晰，即是問當時有沒有警員以警棍打人，朱說無，後來又補充「就我所見無，我睇唔哂成個現場。」<br />\n<br />\n【11:10】<br />\n朱經緯自辯又指，當晚人群聚集後突然多了人過馬路，有人在馬路上跌散紙，也有人在馬路上綁鞋帶，人潮要五至六次轉紅綠燈才能散去。朱指人潮有倒灌情況，警方要出手欄住人潮不准他們過馬路，讓車輛通過。朱用重語氣強調「我」好快發現市民企圖組成「人肉障礙」，延誤過馬路，目的是重佔馬路。警方隨即口頭呼籲，其後推市民過馬路。朱語帶埋怨，指當警方推市民過馬路時，市民會有爭執，他們稱「我哋係過馬路，我哋係路過」。警方認為愈來愈難控制人群，決定將彌郭道及亞皆老街過路口全線封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n朱指封路前，其實人群的行為只是講粗口嗌口號，未有衝突發生，用警方述語即「passive aggression」；封路後人群變得情緒高漲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171109/57436319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57436319&d=jSwC3uiGN3vC7JBO22xqb10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=151fa9f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57436319&h=02e655f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171109/57436319</a>"},{"pid":"e8138034fb4eb541586fb923b57102dfa417fdc4","tid":462904,"uid":47042,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"自殺式作供，完架喇。<br />\n<br />\n差在會唔會判入獄，或者又即時保釋等候上訴。"},{"pid":"7058bd03f5e7778012441be1e59c122fac3aafb7","tid":462904,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:01:46.000Z","msg":"朱sir完全9up<br />\n真係好自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056b63255b4b98947aaaa1400b6d5993f503ef1b","tid":462904,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:08:04.000Z","msg":"其他警員有冇我就唔知，但你就有片有真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a3899f791f744bef2ec73fe41074f2d612a4ef","tid":462904,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朱sir完全9up<br />\n真係好自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前冇人judge佢呀嘛咪唔知自己有幾ON9囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4df48d3645d5e9c0b5787c7057af31095246f0","tid":462904,"uid":126177,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"真係自殺式作供，前言不對後語，個律師冇教佢㗎？"},{"pid":"275086a5ac865ca2a55c80c3339ce3b9c8673d35","tid":462904,"uid":153906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:13:23.000Z","msg":"正一傻朱嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8be3a55ad97945d52f41ecd076c870626c03e6","tid":462904,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>朱sir完全9up<br />\n真係好自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前冇人judge佢呀嘛咪唔知自己有幾ON9囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做得阿sir真係會智障，慣咗講咩都有人yes sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"